Description: SecuBox Netifyd - Network Intelligence Daemon Dashboard
 Deep Packet Inspection daemon management for netifyd. Provides a web
 dashboard for network flow analysis, protocol detection, application
 classification, and device discovery.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time network flow visualization
  - Protocol and application breakdown
  - Device/host discovery and tracking
  - Bandwidth monitoring per app/device
  - DPI alerts and notifications
 .
 Port Debian bookworm from SecuBox OpenWrt netifyd integration.
